# Bingo Host App — Next.js Migration
# Cursor Agent Rules

## Project Overview
A real-time bingo hosting web application. Hosts manage live games (calling numbers, tracking rounds, managing winners). Players join via a 6-digit code and follow along on their devices with real-time updates. Physical bingo cards are used in-venue; this app is the digital companion.

---

## Tech Stack

| Layer | Choice |
|---|---|
| Framework | Next.js 14+ (App Router) |
| Language | TypeScript (strict mode) |
| Database / Realtime | Firebase (Firestore + Auth) |
| Styling | Tailwind CSS + CSS Variables |
| UI Components | shadcn/ui |
| State Management | Zustand |
| Animations | Framer Motion |
| Forms | React Hook Form + Zod |
| Fonts | Google Fonts via `next/font` |
| Hosting | Vercel |

---

## Design System & Visual Identity

### Aesthetic Direction
Modern, high-energy bingo hall translated into a sleek digital experience. Think: dark ambient base with vivid electric accents — the energy of a live event without the dated clip-art bingo aesthetics. Clean, readable, and fast. Every screen should feel purposeful and polished.

### Color Palette (CSS Variables — define in `globals.css`)
```css
:root {
  --bg-base: #0a0a0f;           /* near-black base */
  --bg-surface: #13131a;        /* card/panel backgrounds */
  --bg-elevated: #1c1c28;       /* elevated surfaces, modals */
  --bg-border: #2a2a3a;         /* subtle borders */

  --accent-primary: #6c63ff;    /* electric violet — primary actions */
  --accent-secondary: #00d4aa;  /* teal-green — success, called numbers */
  --accent-warn: #ff6b6b;       /* coral — undo, danger */
  --accent-gold: #ffd166;       /* gold — prizes, winners */

  --text-primary: #f0f0ff;      /* near-white */
  --text-secondary: #8888aa;    /* muted labels */
  --text-disabled: #44445a;     /* disabled states */

  /* Bingo column colors */
  --col-b: #6c63ff;   /* B — violet */
  --col-i: #00d4aa;   /* I — teal */
  --col-n: #ffd166;   /* N — gold */
  --col-g: #ff6b6b;   /* G — coral */
  --col-o: #a78bfa;   /* O — lavender */
}
```

### Typography
- **Display / Headings:** `Syne` (Google Fonts) — geometric, bold, distinctive
- **Body / UI:** `DM Sans` (Google Fonts) — clean, highly readable at all sizes
- **Monospaced / Numbers:** `JetBrains Mono` — for bingo number displays, game codes
- Never use Inter, Roboto, Arial, or system-ui as primary fonts

### Spacing & Layout
- Use Tailwind spacing scale consistently
- Cards use `rounded-2xl` with subtle `border border-[--bg-border]`
- Shadows: `shadow-[0_4px_24px_rgba(108,99,255,0.12)]` for elevated surfaces
- Game grid and number displays should be generous — large touch targets (min 48x48px)
- Responsive: mobile-first, single column → two column at `md:` → dashboard layout at `lg:`

### Motion Principles (Framer Motion)
- Number called: dramatic pop-in with brief glow pulse on the number ball
- New number appearing in the grid: fade + scale from 0.8 → 1
- Screen transitions: subtle fade-slide (y: 8px → 0)
- Toasts / notifications: slide in from top-right
- No layout-breaking or distracting animations — motion enhances, never distracts
- Respect `prefers-reduced-motion`

